{
  "stem": "3949.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By having the Auschwitz album, I have a picture of her and my-- she's holding my little cousin who was her niece.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're standing right in front of the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And her sister with her-- with her four children was there, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I find another page where my father is-- were selected where he's with my cousin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That group were when we arrived, it was my sister, my aunt--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that-- that's not in the book.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my sister, and the aunt of my would-be sister-in-law-- only the three of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My Aunt Rose, they-- she got killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my future sister-in-law, she, you know, died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Red Cross came, then the first thing they did is they give us sugar, and a little piece of bread-- of course, much better one what we used to-- and water.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was our first meal after two weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they put us back to the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- they cleaned out the train first, what we been.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, because this was in the forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have any other train there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And just so many people they put in one of those cattle train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they didn't lock the doors anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took us into-- I think Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went through Germany, and they-- over there they put us into a regular train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took us to Denmark first, and we stayed there for two days in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And over there, they-- they treated us so good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, they took us with a small boat over to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Swedish government took in the prisoner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could only say the nicest thing about those Swedish people, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They cleaned us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took away all--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
